<div><h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>

<h3>1. What types of CCTV cameras do you install?</h3>
<p>We install a wide range of CCTV cameras, including dome cameras, bullet cameras, PTZ cameras, and IP cameras. We offer both standard and HD quality options to suit your specific security needs.</p>

<h3>2. How long does it take to install a CCTV system?</h3>
<p>The installation time depends on the size and complexity of the system. Typically, a basic installation can be completed within a few hours, while more complex systems might take a full day.</p>

<h3>3. Do you offer warranties on your installations?</h3>
<p>Yes, we offer a standard 3-days warranty on all our CCTV installations. This covers any installation-related issues. Extended warranties can be purchased for additional coverage.</p>

<h3>4. Can I monitor my CCTV system remotely?</h3>
<p>Yes, we offer remote monitoring setup services that allow you to view live footage from your CCTV cameras on your smartphone, tablet, or computer from anywhere in the world.</p>

<h3>5. What happens if my CCTV system malfunctions?</h3>
<p>If your CCTV system malfunctions, our repair services are just a call away. We offer prompt service to diagnose and fix any issues, ensuring minimal downtime for your security system.</p>

<h3>6. How often should I service my CCTV system?</h3>
<p>We recommend servicing your CCTV system at least once a year to ensure it remains in optimal working condition. Regular maintenance helps prevent potential issues and extends the lifespan of your system.</p>

<h3>7. Do you provide customized CCTV solutions?</h3>
<p>Yes, we offer tailored CCTV solutions to meet your unique security needs. Our experts will assess your property and recommend the best camera types, placements, and configurations to maximize security.</p>

<h3>8. What are the costs associated with CCTV repair?</h3>
<p>Our CCTV repair services start at ৳500 per camera for basic repairs. More complex issues, such as parts replacement, may incur additional costs. We provide a detailed quote before any repair work begins.</p>

<h3>9. Can you upgrade my existing CCTV system?</h3>
<p>Absolutely. We offer system upgrades to improve the quality and functionality of your existing CCTV setup. Whether you need higher resolution cameras, additional features, or better storage options, we can help.</p>

